Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Fix camera metadata tags for color space profiles maps

Fix camera metadata tags for color space profiles maps

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [Temporary work around]

Signed-off-by: Stoyan Kushlev <skushlev@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 camera/include/system/camera_metadata_tags.h | 19 ++++++++++++++++++-
 1 file changed, 18 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/camera/include/system/camera_metadata_tags.h b/camera/include/system/camera_metadata_tags.h
index c73950e9..e313ebc7 100644
--- a/camera/include/system/camera_metadata_tags.h
+++ b/camera/include/system/camera_metadata_tags.h
@@ -786,6 +786,7 @@ typedef enum camera_metadata_enum_android_control_scene_mode {
